                                "content": "<p>Answer 4 quick health questions to determine your current CKM stage. This will help tailor your education and medical discussions.</p><div id=\"quiz-mount\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;\"><button class=\"btn btn-primary\" onclick=\"app.startQuiz()\">Start Assessment</button></div>",
                                "expanded": "This self-assessment is for educational purposes. Your official stage should be confirmed by your healthcare provider at MetroWest Medical Center."
