                                "sugar": "HbA1c entering Prediabetes or Diabetes range.",
                                "kidneys": "Trace protein in urine or drop in filtration rate.",
                                "heart": "Pressure climbs; heart walls may start to thicken."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "id": 3,
